name: Bitcoin Fund The
longDescription: The Funds investment objectives are to seek to provide holders of Units (Unit holders) of the Fund with: (a) exposure to digital currency bitcoin (bitcoin) and the daily price movements of the U.S. dollar price of bitcoin; and (b) the opportunity for long-term capital appreciation. To achieve its investment objectives, the Fund invests in long-term holdings of bitcoin, purchased from reputable bitcoin trading platforms and OTC counterparties, in order to provide investors with a convenient, safer alternative to a direct investment in bitcoin.
